  <description>for normalization step</description>

  <command>
    /usr/bin/Rscript /home/exacloud/lustre1/GalaxyinstalledTest/galaxy-dist/tools/tcr_seq/galaxy_tools/calc.scaling.factor/calculate.scaling.factor.R
